snippet: Gonzalo Higuain struck again with a trademark goal to give Serie A leaders Juventus a 1-0 win over AS Roma in a tense top-of-the-table match which put them seven points clear on Saturday....
lead_paragraph: Gonzalo Higuain struck again with a trademark goal to give Serie A leaders Juventus a 1-0 win over AS Roma in a tense top-of-the-table match which put them seven points clear on Saturday.

headline.main: Higuain Strikes Again as Juve Beat Roma in Crunch Match
headline.print_headline: Higuain Strikes Again as Juve Beat Roma in Crunch Match
